<summary><strong>Cursor</strong> — hooks with stop support</summary>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Node.js 18+, Cursor with agent mode.</p>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Install:</strong></p>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>
<p dir="auto">Install context-mode globally:</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-shell notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="npm install -g context-mode"><pre>npm install -g context-mode</pre></div>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">Create <code>.cursor/mcp.json</code> in your project root (or <code>~/.cursor/mcp.json</code> for global):</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-json notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="{
  &quot;mcpServers&quot;: {
    &quot;context-mode&quot;: {
      &quot;command&quot;: &quot;context-mode&quot;
    }
  }
}"><pre>{
  <span class="pl-ent">"mcpServers"</span>: {
    <span class="pl-ent">"context-mode"</span>: {
      <span class="pl-ent">"command"</span>: <span class="pl-s"><span class="pl-pds">"</span>context-mode<span class="pl-pds">"</span></span>
    }
  }
}</pre></div>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">Create <code>.cursor/hooks.json</code> (or <code>~/.cursor/hooks.json</code> for global):</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-json notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="{
  &quot;version&quot;: 1,
  &quot;hooks&quot;: {
    &quot;preToolUse&quot;: [
      {
        &quot;command&quot;: &quot;context-mode hook cursor pretooluse&quot;,
        &quot;matcher&quot;: &quot;Shell|Read|Grep|WebFetch|Task|MCP:ctx_execute|MCP:ctx_execute_file|MCP:ctx_batch_execute&quot;
      }
    ],
    &quot;postToolUse&quot;: [
      {
        &quot;command&quot;: &quot;context-mode hook cursor posttooluse&quot;
      }
    ],
    &quot;stop&quot;: [
      {
        &quot;command&quot;: &quot;context-mode hook cursor stop&quot;
      }
    ]
  }
}"><pre>{
  <span class="pl-ent">"version"</span>: <span class="pl-c1">1</span>,
  <span class="pl-ent">"hooks"</span>: {
    <span class="pl-ent">"preToolUse"</span>: [
      {
        <span class="pl-ent">"command"</span>: <span class="pl-s"><span class="pl-pds">"</span>context-mode hook cursor pretooluse<span class="pl-pds">"</span></span>,
        <span class="pl-ent">"matcher"</span>: <span class="pl-s"><span class="pl-pds">"</span>Shell|Read|Grep|WebFetch|Task|MCP:ctx_execute|MCP:ctx_execute_file|MCP:ctx_batch_execute<span class="pl-pds">"</span></span>
      }
    ],
    <span class="pl-ent">"postToolUse"</span>: [
      {
        <span class="pl-ent">"command"</span>: <span class="pl-s"><span class="pl-pds">"</span>context-mode hook cursor posttooluse<span class="pl-pds">"</span></span>
      }
    ],
    <span class="pl-ent">"stop"</span>: [
      {
        <span class="pl-ent">"command"</span>: <span class="pl-s"><span class="pl-pds">"</span>context-mode hook cursor stop<span class="pl-pds">"</span></span>
      }
    ]
  }
}</pre></div>
<p dir="auto">The <code>preToolUse</code> matcher is optional — without it, the hook fires on all tools. The <code>stop</code> hook fires when the agent turn ends and can send a followup message to continue the loop. <code>afterAgentResponse</code> is also available (fire-and-forget, receives full response text).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">Copy the routing rules file. Cursor lacks a SessionStart hook, so the model needs a rules file for routing awareness:</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-shell notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="mkdir -p .cursor/rules
cp node_modules/context-mode/configs/cursor/context-mode.mdc .cursor/rules/context-mode.mdc"><pre>mkdir -p .cursor/rules
cp node_modules/context-mode/configs/cursor/context-mode.mdc .cursor/rules/context-mode.mdc</pre></div>
</li>
