<p dir="auto"><strong>Verify:</strong> In a Pi session, type <code>ctx stats</code>. Context-mode tools should appear and respond.</p>
<p dir="auto"><strong>Routing:</strong> Automatic. The extension registers all key lifecycle events (<code>tool_call</code>, <code>tool_result</code>, <code>session_start</code>, <code>session_before_compact</code>), providing full session continuity and routing enforcement.</p>
